questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I need your Squarespace Login details Or You have to Invite me Into Your Squarespace Account. you need to provide me with your all content if you have. if you have any design files, you can share them with me, so that we can follow your design.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you Help me to choose the Brand Color, Font & Template?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, As a Professional in Website Design & Development, i provide my clients with the best ideas for their Business. So if you don't know which way to go, be assured i am able to help you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you Provide Content ( Text & Images ) as well?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: if you Don't have any content for now, I am able to build your website with simple generic text, & Professional license-free images, Videos And Graphics. But i am not a Copywriter! if you need a professional copy, please contact a copyrighter.

questionsAndAnswers.question: what if I don't have any content and image?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Ok. Don't worry about it. i'll add dummy content and images on your website. when you have your content just replace the whole content. and most importantly you can easily customize your website very easily.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I Get support after Order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. I'll provide free of cost support. But it's only 10 days after the delivery project.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be responsive?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Of course. your website will be responsive to all devices. and your website will be SEO friendly. and browser-compatible so that your user can see your website properly by any modern browser.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why i Should Choose you?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The Key Thing that makes me different is the ability to build a fully Functional website with an absolute minimum of information. You don't have anything but the general idea and some website you like? That will be enough to get started.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What makes you different?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: All my websites are made with great attention to detail. And apart from that, i have a background in both design and devleopment. i already design and develop about Two Hundred Websites in Wordpress & Squarespace. I use Paid Plugins which help me surpass the limits of Squarespace.
